# Streamlit

> The fastest way to build data apps in Python. Create interactive web applications with pure Python — no frontend experience required.

---

## Overview

Streamlit transforms Python scripts into shareable web apps:
- **Pure Python** — No HTML, CSS, or JavaScript required
- **Reactive** — Widgets automatically trigger reruns
- **Data-native** — Built-in support for pandas, charts, ML
- **Rapid prototyping** — From script to app in minutes

### Why Streamlit?

| Feature | Benefit |
|---------|---------|
| **No frontend code** | Python developers stay productive |
| **Hot reload** | See changes instantly |
| **Widgets** | Buttons, sliders, file uploads built-in |
| **Deployment** | Streamlit Cloud (free tier) |
| **Community** | Rich component ecosystem |

