## Usage in Our Stack

### Archon — Meta-Agent Builder

Streamlit provides the UI for Archon's agent creation workflow:

```python
# archon/app.py
import streamlit as st
from archon.builder import AgentBuilder

st.title("Archon - Agent Builder")

# Agent configuration
agent_name = st.text_input("Agent Name")
model = st.selectbox("Model", ["llama-3.1-70b", "mixtral-8x7b"])
tools = st.multiselect("Tools", ["web_search", "code_exec", "file_ops"])

if st.button("Create Agent"):
    builder = AgentBuilder()
    agent = builder.create(name=agent_name, model=model, tools=tools)
    st.success(f"Created agent: {agent.id}")
```

**Key UI elements:**
- Agent configuration forms
- Tool selection interface
- Real-time agent testing
- Deployment status dashboard

