## Deployment

### Streamlit Cloud

```bash
# Create requirements.txt
streamlit
pandas
...

# Push to GitHub, connect to Streamlit Cloud
```

### Docker

```dockerfile
FROM python:3.11-slim
WORKDIR /app
COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install -r requirements.txt
COPY . .
EXPOSE 8501
CMD ["streamlit", "run", "app.py", "--server.port=8501"]
```

